name: Smita’s Lakeview Restaurant & Bar |Best Fish Thali And Authentic Goan Food|

reviews.review_text: Always go and only go for starters dish as they have best cuisine and taste is good. Atmosphere is fantastic with music and lake view point. Main course like thali are okay type. Regarding service they are good for starters like bringing it  quickly but main course they take lot of time. Regarding parking space you forget. Recommended to bring Two wheeler only. It is  also expensive compare to quantity they provide. Overall is Very Good.

Everything was good, at first we thought bit pricey. But when it comes to table, actual quantity was surprisingly good. Quite place with goan music in background. Mr. Bharat served us overall food and he was friendly and a gentleman.

Hi there , I myself n my fiance visited this place when we came across to the video on instagram. I was craving to have the food from a long time while I was in abroad. Sukumar had served us very professionally. Even the food was on time n it was very mouth watering. To everyone reading this if you come to Goa n don’t visit here b eat chonok thali tho kya kaya my friend. Note :my favourite prawns papadom. Thank you

description:
**Welcome to Smita’s Lakeview Restaurant & Bar: A Culinary Gem in Goa Velha**

Nestled in the picturesque locale of Goa Velha, **Smita’s Lakeview Restaurant & Bar** has firmly established itself as a must-visit spot for lovers of authentic Goan cuisine, boasting an impressive rating of **4.2** from nearly **4,000 reviews**. This culinary hotspot is particularly cherished for its **fish thali** and a selection of succulent seafood dishes, garnering frequent references to favorites like **barramundi** (75 mentions), **mussels** (43 mentions), **kingfish** (42 mentions), and the delightful **rava fry** (42 mentions).

**Ambiance & Design**

As you step into Smita’s, you are immediately greeted by a captivating ambiance that features stunning views of the lake. The restaurant is designed to enhance your dining experience with warm lighting and a comfortable seating arrangement, inviting you to unwind as you savor your meal. Diners have praised the atmosphere as fantastic, often complemented by soothing Goan music playing softly in the background, creating a serene escape from the bustling tourism of Goa. The carefully chosen decor reflects the coastal charm of Goa, marked by earthy tones and local artwork, making it a picturesque spot for both intimate dinners and gatherings.

**Menu & Culinary Experience**

The star of the show at Smita’s is undoubtedly its seafood offerings, with the **fish thali** earning high praise for its generous servings and authentic flavors. Reviewers often commend the quality of the ingredients, which are both fresh and thoughtfully prepared. One diner highlighted their experience with **prawns papadom**, describing it as “mouthwatering,” while others have raved about the presentation and flavor of the appetizers. Though some patrons noted that the main course could take a bit longer to arrive, they often found the wait well worth it, thanks to the delectable dishes served. For those with dietary preferences, the menu boasts a variety of options, ensuring that everyone can find something to delight their palate.

**Customer Experience & Service**

Smita’s prides itself on not just the food, but also the warm service provided by its staff. Many reviewers specifically mentioned the friendliness and professionalism of servers like Mr. Bharat and Sukumar, contributing to the overall positive dining experience. Guests have felt welcomed and well-looked after, with prompt service particularly noted for starters. However, it’s worth considering that during peak hours, the time taken for the main courses may vary, so patience might be needed. Additionally, while feedback suggests that parking can be a challenge, a gentle nudge towards using a two-wheeler has been recommended to simplify access.

**Popularity & Reviews**

The buzz surrounding Smita’s Lakeview Restaurant & Bar is palpable not only in person but also on social media platforms. Many guests express their awe of the dining experience, often sharing appealing shots of their meals, notably the delightful seafood platters. The combination of picturesque lake views, an inviting atmosphere, and mouthwatering cuisine has led to a loyal following among locals and tourists alike, making it a culinary star in Goa.

**Visual Highlights**

The stunning imagery shared by guests highlights the vibrant presentation of dishes, as well as the charming environment of the restaurant. Photos depict beautifully arranged plates filled with an assortment of fresh seafood, which not only tantalizes the taste buds but also the eyes. The visual appeal of the lake view adds an enchanting touch, providing the perfect backdrop for a memorable meal, whether indoors or on the patio.

**Conclusion**

In summary, **Smita’s Lakeview Restaurant & Bar** is a standout destination for those seeking a taste of authentic Goan food amid breathtaking scenery. With its commendable ratings, scrumptious seafood offerings, and inviting atmosphere, it captures the essence of Goa while ensuring guests enjoy a memorable dining experience. If you find yourself in Goa Velha, be sure to stop by and indulge in the culinary delights this remarkable spot has to offer.
